A '''rocket ship''' was one of the earliest forms of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] transport, usually armed with primitive [[Laser/Legends|laser]] weaponry and powered by [[nuclear propulsion]].<ref name="DESB">''[[Dark Empire Sourcebook]]''</ref> [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] traveled to [[Sooma]] on a rocket ship.<ref name="D4">[[Droids (1986) 4|''Droids'' (1986) 4]]</ref>

